|ID|OPERATOR         |NAME        |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
---------------------------------------------------------
|0 |SORT             |            |1       |3           |
|1 |└─TABLE FULL SCAN|t_part_range|1       |3           |
=========================================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
