# issue:39111439 bug10: 创建分区表达式是(abs(tinyint))的range分区表，范围查询时，mysql分区裁剪成功，ob分区裁剪失败
explain select n0,n1,n2 from t_part_range where n0 > -10 and n0 < 10;
Query Plan
=================================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                 |NAME        |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
-----------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |PX COORDINATOR           |            |1       |7           |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR     |:EX10000    |1       |7           |
|2 |  └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR|            |1       |7           |
|3 |    └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |t_part_range|1       |7           |
=================================================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([INTERNAL_FUNCTION(t_part_range.n0, t_part_range.n1, t_part_range.n2)]), filter(nil), rowset=16
  1 - output([INTERNAL_FUNCTION(t_part_range.n0, t_part_range.n1, t_part_range.n2)]), filter(nil), rowset=16
      dop=1
  2 - output([t_part_range.n0], [t_part_range.n1], [t_part_range.n2]), filter(nil), rowset=16
      force partition granule
  3 - output([t_part_range.n0], [t_part_range.n1], [t_part_range.n2]), filter([t_part_range.n0 > -10], [t_part_range.n0 < 10]), rowset=16
